<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>비자 승인 안내</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #27ae60;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #27ae60;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .success-badge {
            background-color: #d4edda;
            color: #155724;
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .visa-details {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            border: 1px solid #27ae60;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .visa-details h3 {
            color: #155724;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 8px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .important-notice {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        }
        .important-notice h3 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #27ae60;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .celebration {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">VietnamVisa24</div>
            <h1 class="title">🎉 비자 승인 완료 안내</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="celebration">🎊✈️🇻🇳</div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <div class="success-badge">✅ 비자 승인 완료</div>
            </div>

            <div class="greeting">
                축하합니다! <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>님
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>신청번호:</strong> {{applicationNumber}}<br>
                <strong>승인일시:</strong> {{approvalDate}}<br>
                <strong>처리기간:</strong> {{processingDays}}일
            </div>

            <p>베트남 비자 신청이 성공적으로 승인되었습니다! 🎉</p>

            <div class="visa-details">
                <h3>📋 승인된 비자 정보</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">비자 종류:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{visaType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">유효기간:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{validityPeriod}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">입국 가능 횟수:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{entryType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">최대 체류 기간:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{maxStayDuration}}</span>
                </div>
                {{#if visaNumber}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">비자 번호:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{visaNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="important-notice">
                <h3>⚠️ 중요 안내사항</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>비자는 입국 보장이 아닌 입국 신청 자격을 의미합니다</li>
                    <li>입국 시 출입국 관리소에서 최종 입국 허가 여부가 결정됩니다</li>
                    <li>여권 유효기간이 6개월 이상 남아있는지 확인해 주세요</li>
                    <li>비자 유효기간 내에 입국하셔야 합니다</li>
                    {{#if additionalRequirements}}
                    <li>{{additionalRequirements}}</li>
                    {{/if}}
                </ul>
            </div>

            {{#if downloadUrl}}
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{downloadUrl}}" class="button">📄 비자 서류 다운로드</a>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">내 신청 현황 확인하기</a>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <strong>즐거운 베트남 여행 되세요! 🌴</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>VietnamVisa24</strong></p>
            <p>📞 1588-0000 | 📧 support@vietnamvisa24.com</p>
            <p>평일 09:00~18:00 (토/일/공휴일 휴무)</p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #95a5a6; margin-top: 15px;">
                본 메일은 발신전용입니다. 문의사항이 있으시면 고객센터로 연락해 주세요.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
